
COMMAND:
   clean spirit

DETAILS:
   Clean spirit provides faster healing for ninjas. The ninja sits down
   in the lotus position and concentrates on her/his body. While cleaning
   spirit the ninja can only perform minor actions such as say, ninja,
   score, help, chat, tell, who, look, ....
   Issue the  'wakeup' command to stop meditating.

COST:
    none

POWER:
   wisdom/level/int/cha based

